%% E115 - AuthGuard flow - F1-13 Frontend Auth
%% Source: docs/design/f1-13-auth-sim.md (E114)
flowchart TB
    Start([User navigates to protected route]) --> Guard[AuthGuard runs]
    Guard --> Check{Token válido?}
    Check -->|Sí| Allow[Allow navigation]
    Allow --> Route([User reaches route])

    Check -->|No| Redirect[Redirect to /login?returnUrl=currentUrl]
    Redirect --> Form[LoginComponent: formulario]
    Form --> Submit[User submits email/password]
    Submit --> API[POST /api/auth/login]
    API --> Success{Success?}
    Success -->|No| Error[Show error, stay on /login]
    Success -->|Sí| Store[Store token + user]
    Store --> Nav[Navigate to returnUrl or /buscar]
    Nav --> Route
